{"tid":2355623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「畫家」刑滿出獄隨即被控暴動罪","createTime":"2021-01-06T08:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T11:25:21.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"efabfa742db01665bebb8013ad05f9b1d3e89eb8","tid":2355623,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:27:04.000Z","msg":"前年 7 月 1 日，有示威者衝擊並闖進立法會大樓，多人事後被拘控，當中包括「佔旺畫家」潘浩超，他被控暴動等五罪，案件今於區域法院再提訊，並押後至 3 月 26 日再訊。辯方指潘就包圍警察總部案被判囚 21 個月，並於上月 24 日服刑完畢，今就被控暴動案申請保釋，法官高勁修經考慮後批准潘保釋，條件包括 2,000 元現金、由甘浩望神父自簽 2,000 元作人事擔保、不得離港、須居於長洲善樂舍並接受監管、每晚 9 時至翌晨 7 時宵禁、每周到指定警署報到 3 次等。"},{"pid":"ecb3c83768e5262713ac2b0b0972a1ef7a53f906","tid":2355623,"uid":41368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478ae9b477469e10b20b5abf0fb62b5535d3f3e0","tid":2355623,"uid":364767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"共產黨和特衰政府 收受香港人的錢<br />\n卻日日挖空心思羅織罪名去陷害香港人"},{"pid":"588de9053e0c0e1f9d5125f03fd1f135fd7c120e","tid":2355623,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ecb3c83768e5262713ac2b0b0972a1ef7a53f906","tid":2355623,"uid":41368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"反送中第一個被捕"},{"pid":"fbb42a7a4a9b99e0de719f00a749dac55b89680b","tid":2355623,"uid":152209,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"唉 班狗真係好撚柒弱智同煩"},{"pid":"4dd5289e939b9031ad0ccc5e2decce1e1ae75cfc","tid":2355623,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"成個政府用盡資源去整死香港人"},{"pid":"4e4924ed4d8192ed1ecdb43a5669343d903e1337","tid":2355623,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"畫家好惨